issue.title: Raise Unit
issue.body: THE BIGGEST FEATURE arrives - unit raised. Unit's members maximum number is 8. now AreYouAlive can work with up to 8 soldiers.

issue.title: UI requires development
issue.body: AreYouAlive's UI really requires development. It would be nice if it had material design.

issue.title: Better data structures
issue.body: I really prefer ArrayList after Array.

issue.title: Password checking requires development
issue.body: Password must be checked on the server-side,not inside the software code.
